    {
      "parameters": {
        "sendTo": "={{ $('Parse + Score Lead').first().json.email }}",
        "subject": "Jouw download: SmartESG Leveranciersbeoordeling",
        "emailType": "html",
        "message": "=<!DOCTYPE html><html><body style=\"font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #0f172a; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 24px;\">\n<div style=\"background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0d3b3b, #0f766e); color: white; padding: 32px 28px; border-radius: 12px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.08em; opacity: 0.85; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 8px;\">SMART ESG</div>\n  <h1 style=\"margin: 0; font-size: 24px; line-height: 1.3;\">Hi {{ $('Parse + Score Lead').first().json.voornaam }},</h1>\n  <p style=\"margin: 12px 0 0; opacity: 0.9;\">Bedankt voor je interesse in de Leveranciersbeoordeling.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div style=\"padding: 28px 8px;\">\n  <p>Zoals beloofd: hieronder vind je de PDF terug. Je kunt 'm direct openen via onderstaande knop.</p>\n\n  <div style=\"margin: 28px 0;\">\n    <a href=\"https://download.smartesg.nl/leveranciersbeoordeling.pdf\" style=\"display: inline-block; background: #0f766e; color: white; padding: 14px 22px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 600;\">📄 Open Leveranciersbeoordeling.pdf</a>\n  </div>\n\n  <p>De beoordeling bevat 11 toetsbare criteria verdeeld over vier thema's:</p>\n  <ul>\n    <li><strong>Kwaliteitsmanagement</strong> — ISO 9001, klachten, audits</li>\n    <li><strong>Duurzaamheid &amp; Milieu</strong> — ISO 14001, CO₂ cradle-to-gate</li>\n    <li><strong>Duurzaamheidsnetwerken &amp; Labels</strong> — EcoVadis, FSC, Lean &amp; Green</li>\n    <li><strong>MVO-Rapportage &amp; Transparantie</strong> — Scope 3, GRI / CDP</li>\n  </ul>\n\n  <p style=\"margin-top: 28px;\">Vragen of zin in een korte sparringsessie? Reply gerust op deze mail.</p>\n  <p style=\"margin-top: 8px;\">Hartelijke groet,<br><strong>Tom Teunisse &amp; Bas</strong><br>SmartESG</p>\n</div>\n\n<hr style=\"border: none; border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0; margin: 24px 0;\">\n<p style=\"font-size: 12px; color: #64748b; text-align: center;\">SmartESG · <a href=\"https://smartesg.nl\" style=\"color: #0f766e;\">smartesg.nl</a> · <a href=\"mailto:info@smartesg.nl\" style=\"color: #0f766e;\">info@smartesg.nl</a></p>\n</body></html>",
        "options": {}
      },
